WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:01.600
It's a zombie apocalypse.

00:00:01.600 --> 00:00:03.920
You're stuck in your
apartment with no way out

00:00:03.920 --> 00:00:05.840
and the WiFi doesn't work.

00:00:05.840 --> 00:00:07.280
Do you think you're gonna survive?

00:00:07.280 --> 00:00:08.400
Because I don't.

00:00:08.400 --> 00:00:10.560
In this video, I'll be
breaking down the mistakes

00:00:10.560 --> 00:00:14.960
made in "#Alive," because
there is no way anyone

00:00:14.960 --> 00:00:17.120
should have survived
this zombie apocalypse.

00:00:17.120 --> 00:00:21.840
(soft music)

00:00:21.840 --> 00:00:22.560
Joon-woo wakes up

00:00:22.560 --> 00:00:24.240
to find his family is out of the home.

00:00:24.240 --> 00:00:26.000
So he does what he always does

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:28.400
live streams and plays
games with his friends.

00:00:28.400 --> 00:00:30.880
Except they tell him to
get off and watch the news

00:00:30.880 --> 00:00:32.640
because everywhere in Korea,

00:00:32.640 --> 00:00:34.400
people are attacking each other

00:00:34.400 --> 00:00:36.960
and a state of emergency
has been declared.

00:00:36.960 --> 00:00:38.240
Okay first things first,

00:00:38.240 --> 00:00:39.840
this guy is obviously a gamer.

00:00:39.840 --> 00:00:42.160
So he might have some in-game
knowledge about surviving.

00:00:42.720 --> 00:00:44.960
Gamers may be cowardly in real life

00:00:44.960 --> 00:00:46.000
but their gamer instincts

00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:47.840
could go a long way in an outbreak.

00:00:47.840 --> 00:00:50.240
Already Joon-woo can see
right outside his window

00:00:50.240 --> 00:00:52.000
how people are freaking out.

00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:54.640
Waves of people are running
out of their apartments

00:00:54.640 --> 00:00:57.040
and already we're seeing signs of zombies.

00:00:57.040 --> 00:00:59.520
People biting each
other, leaping, running.

00:00:59.520 --> 00:01:01.280
This is all happening pretty quickly.

00:01:01.280 --> 00:01:04.080
In this specific case,
don't join the crowd.

00:01:04.080 --> 00:01:06.800
Stay behind, let them
draw as many zombies out

00:01:06.800 --> 00:01:08.320
from your area as possible,

00:01:08.320 --> 00:01:09.920
giving you the chance to live.

00:01:09.920 --> 00:01:11.840
An opportunity later to escape

00:01:11.840 --> 00:01:13.760
with less zombies on the loose.

00:01:13.760 --> 00:01:16.560
Also there's no time for
hugs in the apocalypse.

00:01:16.560 --> 00:01:17.920
Why do people do this?

00:01:17.920 --> 00:01:19.520
Maybe she didn't know she would turn

00:01:19.520 --> 00:01:21.920
but even still, run dammit!

00:01:23.040 --> 00:01:25.680
Joon-woo decides to take
a peek outside of his door

00:01:25.680 --> 00:01:28.160
and his next door
neighbor comes rushing in.

00:01:28.160 --> 00:01:30.800
No warning, he's just
suddenly inside the apartment

00:01:30.800 --> 00:01:33.360
and he's begging Joon-woo to let him stay.

00:01:33.360 --> 00:01:35.200
He's brother got bit, he escaped

00:01:35.200 --> 00:01:37.040
and Joon-woo is having none of this.

00:01:37.040 --> 00:01:39.840
He's telling this guy
to get out and go away.

00:01:39.840 --> 00:01:41.120
But he let's his neighbor stay

00:01:41.120 --> 00:01:42.960
long enough to use the bathroom.

00:01:42.960 --> 00:01:44.480
As the guy is there though

00:01:44.480 --> 00:01:45.920
Joon-woo hears on the news

00:01:45.920 --> 00:01:48.240
the symptoms of zombification.

00:01:48.240 --> 00:01:50.560
Bleeding from the eyes, becoming violent,

00:01:50.560 --> 00:01:52.560
and wanting to eat people.

00:01:52.560 --> 00:01:54.160
It gets Joon-woo's thinking

00:01:54.160 --> 00:01:56.080
and he immediately grabs a knife.

00:01:56.080 --> 00:01:58.000
As the neighbor comes out of the bathroom,

00:01:58.000 --> 00:02:00.880
Joon-woo spots a bite mark on his hand

00:02:00.880 --> 00:02:02.800
and forces him out at knife point,

00:02:02.800 --> 00:02:05.280
but the man stops as he reaches the door.

00:02:05.280 --> 00:02:07.360
He begins to turn.

00:02:07.360 --> 00:02:08.880
Look, it doesn't take a genius

00:02:08.880 --> 00:02:10.480
to figure out bite equals bad.

00:02:10.480 --> 00:02:12.480
So when a guy wants to stay in your house

00:02:12.480 --> 00:02:14.800
which you obviously should never do.

00:02:14.800 --> 00:02:17.520
At the very least make
him take his clothes off

00:02:17.520 --> 00:02:19.520
and prove he has no bites on him.

00:02:19.520 --> 00:02:21.120
Not gay if it saves your life.

00:02:21.120 --> 00:02:23.760
I mean the guy's got blood on his shirt.

00:02:23.760 --> 00:02:25.760
You might have better chances of survival

00:02:25.760 --> 00:02:28.640
but if he won't show you,
you gotta go for the knife.

00:02:29.280 --> 00:02:31.040
Violently jerking and cracking,

00:02:31.040 --> 00:02:32.960
the new zombie rushes at Joon-woo

00:02:32.960 --> 00:02:34.720
who gets him to like a bear hug

00:02:34.720 --> 00:02:36.640
and pushes him out of the house.

00:02:36.640 --> 00:02:38.960
Where another zombie
beats the crap out of him.

00:02:40.960 --> 00:02:42.400
That night, Joon-woo blocks

00:02:42.400 --> 00:02:43.760
the front door with a fridge

00:02:43.760 --> 00:02:44.880
and tries to make a call,

00:02:44.880 --> 00:02:46.800
but he can't connect to anyone.

00:02:46.800 --> 00:02:49.440
A news report in TV suggests survivors

00:02:49.440 --> 00:02:51.920
make sure they have
enough food for 60 days

00:02:51.920 --> 00:02:54.320
and Joon-woo starts to
tally up what he has,

00:02:54.320 --> 00:02:55.360
though it doesn't look like

00:02:55.360 --> 00:02:57.520
he has enough for even 10 days.

00:02:57.520 --> 00:02:59.440
Beer will tide you over for a little while

00:02:59.440 --> 00:03:00.800
and nobody will be delivering

00:03:00.800 --> 00:03:02.400
your favorite barbecue chicken.

00:03:02.400 --> 00:03:03.760
Once you lock down your house

00:03:03.760 --> 00:03:05.920
the first thing to do is
ration what you have left

00:03:05.920 --> 00:03:07.360
for as long as you can.

00:03:07.360 --> 00:03:10.480
Then devise a strategy for
getting more food safely.

00:03:10.480 --> 00:03:12.400
If you have any fruit, keep the seeds

00:03:12.400 --> 00:03:14.000
and plant them in flowerpots.

00:03:14.000 --> 00:03:15.280
Water will soon be gone,

00:03:15.280 --> 00:03:17.680
so I'd fill all my containers and tubs

00:03:17.680 --> 00:03:19.200
with tap water to drink.

00:03:19.200 --> 00:03:21.600
This buys me time for a
more long-term solution,

00:03:21.600 --> 00:03:23.120
or at least until it rains.

00:03:23.120 --> 00:03:25.600
Begin cardio endurance
training immediately.

00:03:25.600 --> 00:03:28.000
Gamers are not world-renowned
for their fitness.

00:03:28.000 --> 00:03:31.840
Social media is great, but
here it gets you killed.

00:03:31.840 --> 00:03:34.240
The next day he gets inspired
to check out Instagram

00:03:34.240 --> 00:03:36.160
where people are posting,
calling for help,

00:03:36.160 --> 00:03:37.520
and telling others where they are

00:03:37.520 --> 00:03:39.840
as calls still aren't connecting.

00:03:39.840 --> 00:03:42.880
It's time to use your tech for
survival and not for likes.

00:03:42.880 --> 00:03:43.840
The guy figures out that

00:03:43.840 --> 00:03:45.440
by attaching his phone to a drone,

00:03:45.440 --> 00:03:47.520
he could fly it high
enough to get service.

00:03:47.520 --> 00:03:50.000
He gets a signal and it actually works.

00:03:50.000 --> 00:03:53.120
The call goes through until
he runs out of batteries.

00:03:53.120 --> 00:03:55.040
Charge your batteries first, come on man.

00:03:55.680 --> 00:03:57.840
Scouting the area is the only way to know

00:03:57.840 --> 00:03:59.920
when and how to get out of your flat.

00:03:59.920 --> 00:04:01.200
You'll be able to use this

00:04:01.200 --> 00:04:02.720
to observe your neighbors houses,

00:04:02.720 --> 00:04:05.040
to pick your best future scavenging sites.

00:04:05.040 --> 00:04:07.440
It's not inconceivable
to rappel yourself down

00:04:07.440 --> 00:04:08.800
or climb out to balconies,

00:04:08.800 --> 00:04:11.120
if you know there aren't
immediate threat inside.

00:04:11.120 --> 00:04:12.480
That night a police woman

00:04:12.480 --> 00:04:13.680
runs through his neighborhood,

00:04:13.680 --> 00:04:15.680
drops her gun and gets bitten.

00:04:16.320 --> 00:04:18.800
Even as Joon-woo tries
to distract the zombies

00:04:18.800 --> 00:04:21.040
he can do nothing but
watch as they take her.

00:04:21.680 --> 00:04:23.040
A dropped gun on the streets

00:04:23.040 --> 00:04:24.880
might be enough to lure some outside

00:04:24.880 --> 00:04:26.640
but it's a terrible idea.

00:04:26.640 --> 00:04:28.560
You have no idea how many bullets are left

00:04:28.560 --> 00:04:30.400
so it could leave you dead.

00:04:30.400 --> 00:04:32.000
Also screaming at your windows

00:04:32.000 --> 00:04:33.600
will piss off your neighbors,

00:04:33.600 --> 00:04:35.760
especially the ones with anger problems.

00:04:35.760 --> 00:04:38.000
How the hell did this guy even get inside?

00:04:38.000 --> 00:04:40.400
This big one somehow lumbers its way in

00:04:40.400 --> 00:04:43.120
and it's only by hanging
from his balcony railing

00:04:43.120 --> 00:04:44.640
does Joon-woo trick the zombie

00:04:44.640 --> 00:04:46.240
into falling to it's death.

00:04:46.240 --> 00:04:47.840
Clever, but risky.

00:04:47.840 --> 00:04:49.280
I would have gone for the knife.

00:04:49.280 --> 00:04:50.480
There's no way to know the zombie

00:04:50.480 --> 00:04:52.080
would have flown out the balcony

00:04:52.080 --> 00:04:53.680
without some movie magic.

00:04:53.680 --> 00:04:54.880
It could easily have been you

00:04:54.880 --> 00:04:56.960
lying there with your head bashed in.

00:04:56.960 --> 00:04:59.040
The best solution here is the face off,

00:04:59.040 --> 00:05:00.320
fight it, and aim for the head.

00:05:00.960 --> 00:05:02.960
He fills in the door
to make it more secure

00:05:02.960 --> 00:05:05.040
and starts the first in a series of vlogs

00:05:05.040 --> 00:05:06.720
recording his experiences.

00:05:06.720 --> 00:05:08.720
It's day seven, and Joon-woo learns

00:05:08.720 --> 00:05:11.200
that the zombies infect
others through the blood

00:05:11.200 --> 00:05:12.640
and that they keep some of their memories

00:05:12.640 --> 00:05:14.720
like opening doors or windows.

00:05:14.720 --> 00:05:16.080
He's also desperate,

00:05:16.080 --> 00:05:18.080
the water in his unit no longer works

00:05:18.080 --> 00:05:20.320
and he's downing bottles
of whiskey and beer

00:05:20.320 --> 00:05:21.920
like his liver can afford it.

00:05:21.920 --> 00:05:24.240
While some might think
this is irresponsible

00:05:24.240 --> 00:05:26.320
we should acknowledge the stress involved.

00:05:26.320 --> 00:05:27.760
As far as solutions go,

00:05:27.760 --> 00:05:29.760
whiskey is among the best out there.

00:05:29.760 --> 00:05:32.400
We're not just staying alive,
we're trying to survive.

00:05:32.400 --> 00:05:34.560
That means a little fun can go a long way.

00:05:35.200 --> 00:05:37.360
Still this desperation
doesn't stop Joon-woo

00:05:37.360 --> 00:05:39.120
from taking some safety precautions

00:05:39.120 --> 00:05:41.280
by covering and taping his windows up.

00:05:41.280 --> 00:05:42.880
This might seem like a good idea

00:05:42.880 --> 00:05:44.720
but you're taking away your ability

00:05:44.720 --> 00:05:48.000
to observe your environment
and the zombies themselves.

00:05:48.000 --> 00:05:49.760
I would be conducting experiments

00:05:49.760 --> 00:05:52.080
to learn more about them,
what they respond to.

00:05:52.080 --> 00:05:53.200
Are they out at night?

00:05:53.200 --> 00:05:54.240
What are their habits?

00:05:54.240 --> 00:05:56.880
Anything I can think of
to gain the upper hand.

00:05:56.880 --> 00:05:58.320
In a zombie apocalypse

00:05:58.320 --> 00:06:01.280
ignorance is not bliss, it's death.

00:06:01.280 --> 00:06:03.520
On day 10, he finds
that there's a phone app

00:06:03.520 --> 00:06:05.520
that could let him call using FM waves

00:06:05.520 --> 00:06:07.760
but he needs a specific audio Jack

00:06:07.760 --> 00:06:09.360
which she doesn't have.

00:06:09.360 --> 00:06:12.400
On day 15, Joon-woo gets a
voice message from his dad

00:06:12.400 --> 00:06:15.120
but he still can get a
signal to listen to it.

00:06:15.120 --> 00:06:17.040
He hang off the balcony to get reception,

00:06:17.040 --> 00:06:18.720
grab the attention of the zombies

00:06:18.720 --> 00:06:20.400
who start crowding down below him.

00:06:20.400 --> 00:06:22.000
It's like dinner and a show.

00:06:22.000 --> 00:06:23.600
This gives me a great idea.

00:06:23.600 --> 00:06:26.240
Find the most indestructible
object in your house

00:06:26.240 --> 00:06:27.920
and as much string as you can find.

00:06:27.920 --> 00:06:29.680
Shoelaces, knotted bedsheets

00:06:29.680 --> 00:06:31.120
throw to the zombies below

00:06:31.120 --> 00:06:34.000
aiming to crush their
heads and reel it back up.

00:06:34.000 --> 00:06:35.600
You can take them out one by one

00:06:35.600 --> 00:06:37.040
until you've cleared as many zombies

00:06:37.040 --> 00:06:38.160
from the area as possible.

00:06:39.600 --> 00:06:41.280
Nevermind, this is better

00:06:41.280 --> 00:06:43.360
let's just wing this whole survivor thing.

00:06:43.360 --> 00:06:45.760
Looks like gamer strategy
flew out the window.

00:06:45.760 --> 00:06:48.320
He leaves this apartment
and when he cuts a corner

00:06:48.320 --> 00:06:50.880
he sees his zombified
neighbor crawling around.

00:06:51.760 --> 00:06:53.120
Why does he keep shouting?

00:06:53.120 --> 00:06:54.640
Adrenaline is good for killing

00:06:54.640 --> 00:06:57.360
but don't use it to draw
more attention to yourself

00:06:57.360 --> 00:06:59.040
especially if you're using it

00:06:59.040 --> 00:07:00.800
to trash talk a zombie.

00:07:00.800 --> 00:07:02.480
And then more zombies show up

00:07:02.480 --> 00:07:05.440
closing in on him from
both sides of the complex.

00:07:05.440 --> 00:07:06.640
He goes through the elevator

00:07:06.640 --> 00:07:08.800
but a whole crowd of zombies fall out.

00:07:09.440 --> 00:07:12.320
Also elevators very bad idea.

00:07:12.320 --> 00:07:14.400
I hate waiting for them in normal time

00:07:14.400 --> 00:07:16.880
during the zombie
apocalypse, I can't even.

00:07:16.880 --> 00:07:18.160
He sneaks his way back up

00:07:18.160 --> 00:07:19.920
