On day 20 the power plants
in the city blow up.

00:07:40.080 --> 00:07:42.720
Everywhere buildings
are losing electricity

00:07:42.720 --> 00:07:45.680
and Joon-woo decides to finally give up.

00:07:46.560 --> 00:07:49.040
He tries to go out like
Epstein by hanging himself,

00:07:49.040 --> 00:07:52.080
but as he's choking someone
shines a laser on him.

00:07:52.080 --> 00:07:53.520
He wriggles out of his noose

00:07:53.520 --> 00:07:56.160
and sees directly across
from his building,

00:07:56.160 --> 00:07:57.680
who is pointing the laser.

00:07:57.680 --> 00:08:00.720
This chick is Yoo-bin,
who is honestly a bad-ass.

00:08:00.720 --> 00:08:03.200
She's very well-prepared
to survive with supplies,

00:08:03.200 --> 00:08:05.200
a good sense to ration what she has,

00:08:05.200 --> 00:08:07.840
and she's even set up a
trap in front of her door

00:08:07.840 --> 00:08:09.520
in case something comes in.

00:08:09.520 --> 00:08:11.760
She has also been scouting
the various floors

00:08:11.760 --> 00:08:12.800
in Joon-woo's apartment

00:08:12.800 --> 00:08:14.560
spotting which ones are full zombies,

00:08:14.560 --> 00:08:15.600
and which ones aren't.

00:08:15.600 --> 00:08:16.800
They tell each other their names

00:08:16.800 --> 00:08:18.640
and Joon-woo seems to
think she's pretty cute.

