but if you are this bad at surviving

00:08:33.520 --> 00:08:34.960
that's all the hope you've got.

00:08:34.960 --> 00:08:36.800
She sees that Joon-woo is starving,

00:08:36.800 --> 00:08:38.640
so she tries tossing over a rope

00:08:38.640 --> 00:08:40.560
which absolutely fails.

00:08:40.560 --> 00:08:42.400
This rope falls to the streets

00:08:42.400 --> 00:08:45.760
