00:08:57.280 --> 00:09:00.080
Which in any other zombie
apocalypse is no problem

00:09:00.080 --> 00:09:03.280
but zombies here retain
some of their memories.

00:09:03.280 --> 00:09:05.040
Now this rope is connected to a table

00:09:05.040 --> 00:09:06.320
and because it's being pulled,

00:09:06.320 --> 00:09:08.640
it violently knocks out Yoo-bin.

00:09:08.640 --> 00:09:10.640
A climbing zombie is definitely a first

00:09:10.640 --> 00:09:12.560
but it's not the time to be impressed.

00:09:12.560 --> 00:09:15.040
Your future ex-girlfriend
is in serious trouble

00:09:15.040 --> 00:09:16.640
and now's the time to figure out

00:09:16.640 --> 00:09:18.800
how to ruin everything fast.

00:09:18.800 --> 00:09:20.080
Joon-woo does everything he can

00:09:20.080 --> 00:09:21.680
to distract the firefighter.

00:09:21.680 --> 00:09:23.040
Shouting, throwing bottles

00:09:23.040 --> 00:09:24.320
and he ends up using his drone

00:09:24.320 --> 00:09:26.160
which the firefighter breaks.

00:09:26.160 --> 00:09:27.520
The drone is great thinking.

00:09:27.520 --> 00:09:29.520
It perfectly combines what you're good at

00:09:29.520 --> 00:09:30.320
and what you can use

00:09:30.320 --> 00:09:32.800
to immediately influence a situation.

00:09:32.800 --> 00:09:34.720
But I would have gone one step further

00:09:34.720 --> 00:09:36.240
and attached a knife to the drone.

00:09:36.240 --> 00:09:38.160
It might not be fast enough to stab it

00:09:38.160 --> 00:09:40.400
but it would give your new
friend a fighting chance

00:09:40.400 --> 00:09:41.920
if she didn't have a weapon.

00:09:41.920 --> 00:09:43.920
It's by sheer luck that
Yoo-bin gets up in time

00:09:43.920 --> 00:09:45.840
to cut off the firefighters hand

00:09:45.840 --> 00:09:47.760
sending it plummeting to the ground.

