and go scavenging for
food and other things.

00:09:51.040 --> 00:09:52.960
Breaking into his next
door neighbor's house,

00:09:52.960 --> 00:09:55.200
which is filled with food, walkie-talkies,

00:09:55.200 --> 00:09:57.840
mountaineering gear and
of course a dead body.

00:09:57.840 --> 00:10:00.080
Joon-woo checks to see who the body is

00:10:00.080 --> 00:10:03.120
and it's a random woman, which is weird

00:10:03.120 --> 00:10:05.520
since his neighbor's brother was infected.

00:10:05.520 --> 00:10:07.200
So where's he?

00:10:07.200 --> 00:10:08.800
As soon as Joon-woo finds this out

00:10:08.800 --> 00:10:10.800
the zombified brother attacks him,

00:10:10.800 --> 00:10:13.040
and it's only thanks to
some quick thinking and luck

00:10:13.040 --> 00:10:14.320
that Joon-woo gets out.

00:10:16.800 --> 00:10:19.680
Sharing a walkie-talkie
and Nutella with Yoo-bin.

00:10:19.680 --> 00:10:21.440
The next day they notice that the zombies

00:10:21.440 --> 00:10:24.080
are suddenly running through
both apartment complexes.

00:10:24.080 --> 00:10:25.040
They don't know why.

00:10:25.040 --> 00:10:26.960
As Yoo-bin goes to grab her hatchet

00:10:26.960 --> 00:10:29.760
she accidentally knocks over a table.

00:10:29.760 --> 00:10:31.360
The whole conga line of zombies

00:10:31.360 --> 00:10:33.760
make their way to a room
but they get distracted

00:10:33.760 --> 00:10:35.680
as Joon-woo calls the landline

00:10:35.680 --> 00:10:37.440
of the unit next to Yoo-bin's.

00:10:37.440 --> 00:10:38.880
The ringing of the neighbor's phone,

00:10:38.880 --> 00:10:40.560
drawing away the zombie horde.

00:10:40.560 --> 00:10:42.080
Calling your neighbor's phone is smart

00:10:42.080 --> 00:10:44.560
but it's life or death riding on one idea.

00:10:44.560 --> 00:10:46.800
Herds are a problem you
can't solve in the moment.

00:10:46.800 --> 00:10:49.440
Your only option is to
hide and draw no attention

00:10:49.440 --> 00:10:50.400
but they can be avoided

00:10:50.400 --> 00:10:52.400
with some organization and planning.

00:10:52.400 --> 00:10:54.640
The best advantage is
that you are in a building

00:10:54.640 --> 00:10:56.080
with sealable entrances.

00:10:56.080 --> 00:10:57.680
If you could start by clearing your floor

00:10:57.680 --> 00:10:58.960
and work with reliable neighbors,

00:10:58.960 --> 00:11:00.160
to clear the building slowly,

00:11:00.160 --> 00:11:02.160
it's a realistic way to
take back the building

00:11:02.160 --> 00:11:03.520
and barricade the main entrances.

00:11:03.520 --> 00:11:05.440
But if it's just too daunting a task

00:11:05.440 --> 00:11:07.360
it's still worthwhile
to create sound traps,

00:11:07.360 --> 00:11:09.120
to distract zombies away from you.

00:11:09.120 --> 00:11:10.640
Pots and pans work well for this.

00:11:10.640 --> 00:11:11.840
Lower them to the floor below

00:11:11.840 --> 00:11:13.600
attached to a string and pull it

00:11:13.600 --> 00:11:15.280
when a distraction is required.

00:11:15.280 --> 00:11:16.960
They both decide that
now is the only chance

00:11:16.960 --> 00:11:18.960
to get to the eighth floor and gear up.

00:11:18.960 --> 00:11:21.440
Joon-woo tries to coordinate
and come up with a plan

00:11:21.440 --> 00:11:23.840
but Yoo-bin pulls a mission impossible.

00:11:23.840 --> 00:11:25.680
Sliding down a rope from her balcony

00:11:25.680 --> 00:11:28.080
and making a mad dash
to Joon-woo's apartment

00:11:28.080 --> 00:11:30.080
and she does an amazing job by the way.

00:11:30.080 --> 00:11:31.440
She's bobbing and weaving,

00:11:31.440 --> 00:11:33.040
beating the crap out of any zombie

00:11:33.040 --> 00:11:34.240
with her climbing acts.

00:11:34.240 --> 00:11:36.160
But her ankle gets caught by a zombie

00:11:36.160 --> 00:11:37.680
and she barely grabs the pistol

00:11:37.680 --> 00:11:38.960
that's been left out here,

00:11:38.960 --> 00:11:40.800
as Joon-woo comes down to help her.

00:11:40.800 --> 00:11:44.000
Jumping into a parking lot
of zombies is a terrible idea

00:11:44.000 --> 00:11:46.400
but if you must, don't try to kill them.

00:11:46.400 --> 00:11:49.360
All survival now depends on
invasion, to move forward

00:11:49.360 --> 00:11:51.280
and out of the growing cluster of zombies

00:11:51.280 --> 00:11:52.960
where you can easily be trapped,

00:11:52.960 --> 00:11:54.800
if spent hacking away at one.

00:11:54.800 --> 00:11:58.080
Football players would do
well, golfers would not.

00:11:58.080 --> 00:12:00.560
The two survivors run back
into Joon-woo's building

00:12:00.560 --> 00:12:02.880
and take the elevator to the eighth floor.

00:12:02.880 --> 00:12:05.280
The zombies stampede into the lobby.

00:12:05.280 --> 00:12:07.680
Upstairs, the doors of
the apartments are locked

00:12:07.680 --> 00:12:10.880
and a whole mob of the
undead finds the two humans.

00:12:10.880 --> 00:12:12.080
The two of them desperately

00:12:12.080 --> 00:12:13.280
try to unlock the apartments

00:12:13.280 --> 00:12:14.640
and are saved by this man

00:12:14.640 --> 00:12:16.160
who drags them inside his unit.

00:12:19.120 --> 00:12:20.720
He shares with them food and water

00:12:20.720 --> 00:12:23.520
and tells them supposedly
there are teams of soldiers

00:12:23.520 --> 00:12:25.360
flying around the city to rescue people,

00:12:25.360 --> 00:12:27.600
and there should be one
arriving sometime soon.

00:12:27.600 --> 00:12:28.880
Great news for everyone

00:12:28.880 --> 00:12:31.200
if they're actually going
to make it out alive.

00:12:31.200 --> 00:12:33.360
Yoo-bin and Joon-woo do
everything right here.

00:12:33.360 --> 00:12:34.880
They wait until the guy drinks the water

00:12:34.880 --> 00:12:36.080
to see if it's dangerous

00:12:36.080 --> 00:12:38.160
and then they asked for canned goods,

00:12:38.160 --> 00:12:40.240
which would have signs
of being tampered with.

00:12:40.240 --> 00:12:42.960
Honestly, I don't think
I'd do anything differently

00:12:42.960 --> 00:12:45.520
but how exactly did the
guy poisoned the food?

00:12:45.520 --> 00:12:47.840
This guy not only didn't
have a lease in this unit

00:12:47.840 --> 00:12:50.480
but he drugs and zip ties
Joon-woo and Yoo-bin,

00:12:50.480 --> 00:12:52.720
as he intends to feed them to his wife.

00:12:52.720 --> 00:12:54.160
No, she's not a cannibal

00:12:54.160 --> 00:12:56.080
she's a zombified freak on a leash,

00:12:56.080 --> 00:12:58.000
who the man locks in a nursery room.

00:12:58.000 --> 00:13:00.240
There is no way she's getting out of here

00:13:00.240 --> 00:13:01.920
but Joon-woo is able to wake up

00:13:01.920 --> 00:13:03.600
and threaten the man with the gun.

00:13:03.600 --> 00:13:05.600
He tries again to let Yoo-bin out

00:13:05.600 --> 00:13:08.000
but the man instead let's go to the leash

00:13:08.000 --> 00:13:10.320
letting his zombified wife attack Yoo-bin

00:13:10.320 --> 00:13:12.960
who's screams go totally silent.

00:13:12.960 --> 00:13:14.320
The kidnapper unlocks the door

00:13:14.320 --> 00:13:15.440
to find out what happened,

00:13:15.440 --> 00:13:16.480
only to find his wife

00:13:16.480 --> 00:13:18.320
being pushed out the door by Yoo-bin.

00:13:18.320 --> 00:13:21.360
The zombie immediately
latching onto her husband,

00:13:21.360 --> 00:13:24.320
biting and nibbling him
as he apologizes to her

00:13:24.320 --> 00:13:27.200
but not the two people he
just tried to kill, classy.

00:13:27.760 --> 00:13:29.520
Yoo-bin uses one bullet

00:13:29.520 --> 00:13:33.440
to take out both of them
and alerts the horde.

00:13:33.440 --> 00:13:36.000
Shooting a gun in a zombie
apocalypse is dangerous

00:13:36.000 --> 00:13:37.600
but if you had to use the gun,

00:13:37.600 --> 00:13:39.760
it would have been smarter
to just shoot the guy.

00:13:39.760 --> 00:13:41.840
We're obviously not gonna
convince him to stop

00:13:41.840 --> 00:13:44.000
if there's more than one
bullet left in the gun

00:13:44.000 --> 00:13:46.080
shoot the lock off and
forget about the key.

00:13:46.080 --> 00:13:47.360
Every second is precious

00:13:47.360 --> 00:13:48.880
if you're trying to save your girlfriend

00:13:48.880 --> 00:13:50.960
from imminent face munch by zombie.

00:13:50.960 --> 00:13:52.320
She begs Joon-woo to take her out

00:13:52.320 --> 00:13:54.080
and he agrees just about ready

00:13:54.080 --> 00:13:55.760
to blow her mind with his piece,

00:13:55.760 --> 00:13:58.640
when he hears what
sounds like helicopters.

00:13:59.280 --> 00:14:01.040
Immediately the two survivors

00:14:01.040 --> 00:14:03.360
rush to the rooftop, tearing past zombies

00:14:03.360 --> 00:14:04.800
and trying to slow down the mob

00:14:04.800 --> 00:14:08.080
but by the time they get up
there, no one is waiting.

00:14:08.080 --> 00:14:09.680
Now they're well and truly dead

00:14:09.680 --> 00:14:11.920
as zombies break through
the door and bum-rush them.

00:14:11.920 --> 00:14:12.960
There was no escape

00:14:12.960 --> 00:14:15.120
and the gun just ran out of amour.

00:14:15.120 --> 00:14:16.720
There is no way out,

00:14:16.720 --> 00:14:19.920
except as you probably
figured out by now, there is.

00:14:19.920 --> 00:14:21.920
A helicopter of armed soldiers

00:14:21.920 --> 00:14:23.440
shows up out of nowhere,

00:14:23.440 --> 00:14:24.960
taking the two survivors on board,

00:14:24.960 --> 00:14:27.520
where Joon-woo begins to
receive a signal on his phone

00:14:27.520 --> 00:14:29.920
and finds out his family are still alive.

00:14:29.920 --> 00:14:32.400
Joon-woo is just one of
many Koreans who were saved

00:14:32.400 --> 00:14:34.000
as everywhere throughout the city,

00:14:34.000 --> 00:14:35.920
survivors are posting to social media

00:14:35.920 --> 00:14:37.840
about where they are and in turn,

00:14:37.840 --> 00:14:39.840
soldiers are coming to rescue them.

00:14:39.840 --> 00:14:41.760
And here I thought
social media was useless.

00:14:42.400 --> 00:14:43.920
Who knew that it could save your life,

